## File yang Dibuat/Dimodifikasi

| File | Keterangan |
|------|-----------|
| [.env](file:///Users/macbook/Documents/WORK%20/WebAudit-Azis/WebsiteAudit-Client-Assistance-Schedule/.env) | Konfigurasi MySQL |
| [bootstrap/app.php](file:///Users/macbook/Documents/WORK%20/WebAudit-Azis/WebsiteAudit-Client-Assistance-Schedule/bootstrap/app.php) | Middleware registration |
| [routes/web.php](file:///Users/macbook/Documents/WORK%20/WebAudit-Azis/WebsiteAudit-Client-Assistance-Schedule/routes/web.php) | Routing lengkap |
| [resources/css/app.css](file:///Users/macbook/Documents/WORK%20/WebAudit-Azis/WebsiteAudit-Client-Assistance-Schedule/resources/css/app.css) | Desain premium 229 baris |
| [resources/views/layouts/app.blade.php](file:///Users/macbook/Documents/WORK%20/WebAudit-Azis/WebsiteAudit-Client-Assistance-Schedule/resources/views/layouts/app.blade.php) | Layout utama + sidebar |
| [resources/views/layouts/guest.blade.php](file:///Users/macbook/Documents/WORK%20/WebAudit-Azis/WebsiteAudit-Client-Assistance-Schedule/resources/views/layouts/guest.blade.php) | Layout auth |
| `app/Models/*.php` | 5 model (User, KapProfile, Client, DataRequest, Invitation) |
| `app/Http/Middleware/*.php` | 2 middleware (Auditor, Auditi) |
| `app/Livewire/*.php` | 7 komponen Livewire |
| `resources/views/livewire/*.blade.php` | 7 views Blade |
| `database/migrations/*.php` | 5 file migrasi |

## Cara Menjalankan

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Laravel server
php artisan serve --port=8080

# Terminal 2 — Vite dev server
npm run dev
```

Buka `http://127.0.0.1:8080` di browser.
